title: Worst Date Wednesday: The Whole Family Was There!
description: Morgan tells us of a date she went on with the guy she had a crush on since Kindergarten!  It didn't go as planned, started with him stopping at his family's to help his Uncle move, then him flirting with other people on their date and it gets worse.  Needless to say that she got closure over her young crush.
